<div>Butler Netball is one of the most popular Girl's Sports with two teams that play competitively each week. There is a very relaxed atmosphere for all abilities, whether you just want to come to training or play against other colleges, the more the merrier.</div><div><br /></div><div>There is a taster session on Tuesday 1st October at 4pm on the MUGA (behind Ustinov) for anyone who is interested in coming along and we will be at the Fair on Saturday 5th October where you can sign up!</div><div><br /></div><div>You are also more than welcome to come along to any of our sessions, we train 12-1 Wednesday on the MUGA (behind Ustinov) and 12-1 Saturday in the Howlands as well.&nbsp;</div><div><br /></div><div>If you would like any information or have a question just send Nemmy Johnston n.e.m.johnston@durham.ac.uk or Alex Smith (A Team Captain) alexandra.smith@durham.ac.uk an email.&nbsp;</div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div>